Generation AI
{% endset %}
{% include "blocks/kadence/advancedheading.njk" %}


<blockquote class="wp-block-quote">
<p>In the project, a foundation is being built upon which "AI generation" technology education can be constructed: technology education that takes into account the principles of artificial intelligence, the opportunities it offers and its dynamic impacts—without forgetting its shortcomings and risks or how AI systems can increase polarization, discrimination, insecurity and erode trust. The project supports learners' understanding of safety and trust in artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) based systems.&nbsp;</p>
<cite>Excerpt from the project's situation report. Read more: <a href="https://www.generation-ai-stn.fi/tilannekuva-2022-tiivistelma/" title="Situation Report 2022 – Summary">Situation Report 2022 – Summary</a></cite></blockquote>


